Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以走…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有…好好地…道别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间! 芽间!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}芽间——! 芽间——! 芽间——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 嗯 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 波波 这里是我躲的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间常常会觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波波 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己正在和大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安鸣 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs35}74号大道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs35}主角 芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs35}持有徽章 0个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs35}裤袋妖怪 3只
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs35}游戏时间 1:15
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间没法和朋友交换妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 以选出的小组长为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起组成小组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那边集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间一直觉得自己没法成为大家的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为芽间是被排挤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.16,note,NTP,0,0,0,,注：被排挤的人和裤袋妖怪同音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就跟我们一组了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一组?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次交换到的裤袋妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是皮皮顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 交换完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让芽间出贾古拉斯 你就出皮皮顿?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺负人可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦 是她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽 芽间就要皮皮顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我都说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然芽间没意见 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 皮皮顿的特技是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「大家一起跳舞」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「大家」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是像团子那样的一团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是像米花糖的米一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个一个 粒粒分明的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后团结成一体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是「大家」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤见子 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 鹤见子太好找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有藏好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差仁碳和芽间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳会不会躲在祠堂里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在里面会遭报应的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过仁碳很可能会躲进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳 芽间 找到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:54.95,title_no,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}致芽间的信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鹤见子 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶?嗯 今天6点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你的信写好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道要写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有很多话想对芽间说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写上你必须告诉芽间的话怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么叫必须告诉的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么6点见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤见子老这么高高在上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}给安鸣 最喜欢可靠的安鸣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好像在欺负人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢仁碳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直最喜欢仁碳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 仁碳你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢芽间…吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你 你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就实话实说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「超和平Busters」之间不许有秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 说啊 说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}说啊 快说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}快说 快说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会喜欢这种丑八怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 和芽间分别后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再也无法传达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能传达到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要告诉她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要买裤袋妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 最后一份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真走运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说4600的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把8看成6了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才要是不买果汁就够钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}哦 裤袋妖怪已经出了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就去取钱 请等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下 有裤袋妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不先预订果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去把200补上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只给你1小时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到那家伙是个好人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然叫我「那家伙」 这些臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢 那我就先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点奇怪啊 问你好不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后 我有时去上学 有时逃学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 过得还算马马虎虎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段时间 让打工的前辈带我去了卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没去过那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大家面前唱歌真是相当害臊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一首谁的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}好想见你 好想见你 我的心在颤动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}越是想念你就觉得越遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都用假声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}即使再一次听到谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌曲也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得大家都很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是卡拉OK而已 有点小题大做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能觉得鸡毛蒜皮的事很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对自己不上心 却瞧不起周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你出现…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 才不是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 话说你胸部绝对变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得有点恶心啦 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死去死去死去死 去死去死去死去死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要再把劣质的基因传下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发了情的淫兽们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死 去死 去死…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}啊咧?这个是「建筑工」吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 女人真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～但是很像哦 嘴唇明明那么厚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种理由的话 珠算补习班里的那老头也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…可是啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天的野兽 非常地 凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间也要吃 咸拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 鸡蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间要吃蛋花汤 蛋花汤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋…要凝固了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鸡蛋搅开啦 搅开 搅开…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么啊 拉面?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}是叔叔! 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 仁太也给我做一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}哎? 为什么给叔叔做就不给芽间做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那见啥都说可爱的习惯该改改了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}叔叔之前也有说过芽间的包包很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎? 但这是个好词啊 哪里都能用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不会用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋要什么样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个荷包蛋 不要散咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 连叔叔也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏心 偏心 偏心大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视电视…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猫咪好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸的表现也没有反常 看来果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡椒胡椒胡椒胡椒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筷子在哪儿 筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你怎么了 在家里中暑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱但是…不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间出现在我的面前 这么对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 也许…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间是想来实现愿望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望? 什么愿望?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那个也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望都不知道是什么怎么实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…但是 总觉得就是这样来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…到底是什么愿望呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水飞出来了 真讨厌!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屏障!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}这可是无敌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就是夏天的猛兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}这下芽间无敌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的压力 我的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先把你说的愿望想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对啊 对啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是必须要大家一起才能实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎? 大家是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我强行带到了夏日的阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 都这时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后发生了许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你拉着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是你拉着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 五年的时光还真是很长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是逃避 总是说大家一起实现愿望是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间居然为了让你帮她实现愿望而回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波波第一个相信了你的归来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(通信中 请不要拔掉连接线)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(恭喜 稀有 nokemon 友情之王 诞生了)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉体内停滞的某样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实又开始运转了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 我来换班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间 在吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好都已经投胎了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是到了附近 可要给我打电话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随时都会骑着摩托赶过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不过要是成了小宝宝就打不了电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没法拨号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让妈妈帮你打过来哦 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}(波波 我最喜欢有趣的波波)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间 一直以来 真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直把花放在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开在你那天去的那个地方的花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕 只顾着害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 我觉得把那个带在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对自己的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅自把你当作了可怕的瘟神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 当仁碳说你在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实话说 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我并不完全相信仁碳的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一想到一直想着你的并不只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都看不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就觉得你果然还是在生我的气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才看不见你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 我就闹起了别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在我家吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是带山菜了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是天麸罗好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波波 看上去吃得很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子上面脏了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 芽间在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 在的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间也来吃吧 天麸罗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我后来又仔细想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大概芽间在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概不是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会留在这里吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成…佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种 那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 芽间在那里么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈? 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给一点点提示 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:22:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为你「咚咚咚叮」的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 也依靠一下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 久川
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…不要只在仁碳面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在我的面前现个身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗? 喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}听我说 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}和大家一起来 好好地想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成佛什么的 这些东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}大家一起考虑吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 芽间也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波波!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是想道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.55,0:24:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却让你更悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.22,0:24:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天社团活动结束后还有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.03,0:24:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.20,0:24:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是高一在传说的那个 高二的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.71,0:24:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他发现的话肯定会生气的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.13,0:24:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间 虽然你说我是个努力奋斗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是说实话 我完全不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.80,0:24:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近也没怎么跑步了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.22,0:25:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我并不觉得这是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.35,0:25:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.86,0:25:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许是想通过奔跑去逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.99,0:25:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避没有你在的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.74,0:25:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.34,0:25:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.18,0:25:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.69,0:25:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪 雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.28,0:25:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点儿啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.37,0:25:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿海!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.28,0:26:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.13,0:26:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件…连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.10,0:26:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和芽间穿的那件很像
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.09,0:26:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么穿成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.06,0:26:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.56,0:26:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.11,0:26:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.03,0:26:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看清楚啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.41,0:26:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.03,0:26:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.87,0:26:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.54,0:26:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.91,0:26:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.27,0:26:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这次错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.20,0:26:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.53,0:26:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤见子…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.88,0:26:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.63,0:27:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起来像芽间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.43,0:27:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看见芽间吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.64,0:27:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 看上去像芽间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.72,0:27:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.39,0:27:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底像不像!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.94,0:27:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.19,0:27:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 芽间会死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.73,0:27:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.11,0:27:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.40,0:27:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会是你的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.99,0:27:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如说是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.61,0:27:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说是我的错了!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.20,0:27:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是没对芽间说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.49,0:27:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间就不会死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.58,0:27:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我害死芽间的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.25,0:27:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间要是出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.84,0:27:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该出现在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.46,0:27:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变鬼也好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.42,0:27:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.09,0:27:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.34,0:27:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该在我的面前!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.47,0:27:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.98,0:27:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.10,0:27:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.57,0:27:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.52,0:27:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 芽间已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.82,0:28:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也…不在这个世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.70,0:28:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.17,0:28:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间说「我就在这里」…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.42,0:28:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.13,0:28:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在说那种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.22,0:28:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽…芽间让我对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.64,0:28:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「发夹 谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.06,0:28:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.94,0:28:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.82,0:28:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然不太清楚 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.66,0:28:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.20,0:28:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时候想要给你的发卡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.41,0:28:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给我最喜欢的面码!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.93,0:29:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁 仁碳走掉了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.30,0:29:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间必须去追仁碳 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.77,0:29:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.31,0:29:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.48,0:29:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我不得不相信你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.40,0:29:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.62,0:29:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远也赢不了仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤见子说我装模作样地说这种话很烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.55,0:29:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安鸣则说我绝对不招女孩子喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.01,0:29:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实她们不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.76,0:29:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 都叫你别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起 那个 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.39,0:29:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.69,0:29:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.32,0:30:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.82,0:30:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.33,0:30:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 其实还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.68,0:30:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.89,0:30:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在明明是暑假 你还真让人佩服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.43,0:30:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.22,0:30:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么到学校来了 信写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.57,0:30:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在图书室写的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.42,0:30:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一个人在家里写 搞不好会哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.94,0:30:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.53,0:30:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.82,0:30:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.10,0:30:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.91,0:30:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.66,0:30:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.00,0:31:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.30,0:31:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腿好像要更长点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.87,0:31:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把你画得挺不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.56,0:31:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真严格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.06,0:31:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.71,0:31:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要再画一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.06,0:31:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.69,0:31:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张画 画得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.78,0:31:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.38,0:31:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.86,0:31:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是表扬我的画
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.59,0:31:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我非常喜欢画画
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.03,0:31:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我发现自己无论怎么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.69,0:32:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总还是有瓶颈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我马上就转变了目标
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.03,0:32:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得再画下去也不会留下什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.54,0:32:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是太过多虑
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.96,0:32:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先自己下定结论
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.92,0:32:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪集的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.21,0:32:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直喜欢他 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.13,0:32:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.43,0:32:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得自己赢不了芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.89,0:32:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 在芽间不在了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.73,0:32:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得只要能待在他身边就好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为这就是自己真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.31,0:32:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.37,0:33:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一定不会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.36,0:33:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 听说你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.09,0:33:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕自己会因此动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.47,0:33:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.39,0:33:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 大家也真的相信你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.15,0:33:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}你这家伙！什么nice middle啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.26,0:33:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}不要笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.65,0:33:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我动摇 恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.95,0:33:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.79,0:33:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了 信写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.87,0:33:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在写
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.38,0:33:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.17,0:33:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 鹤见子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.76,0:33:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话想对芽间说
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.10,0:34:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使能传达给她
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.77,0:34:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也还是开不了口对他说
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.14,0:34:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是指仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.28,0:34:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别这样藏着掖着结果又莫名其妙地自爆就好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.35,0:34:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫莫名其妙地自爆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.45,0:34:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说鹤见子你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.32,0:34:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.87,0:34:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是趁乱对雪集表白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.30,0:34:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这说法真失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.66,0:34:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.42,0:34:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事应该还是含含糊糊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.30,0:34:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.42,0:34:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 那也没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.17,0:34:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为雪集都喜欢芽间到能黑化成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.97,0:34:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我轻松了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.31,0:34:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.56,0:34:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.95,0:34:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 都这时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不准备走可能就要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.40,0:34:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也抓紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.87,0:35:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.25,0:35:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的芽间 谢谢你给我的信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.13,0:35:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我很可靠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.13,0:35:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我自己并不这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.97,0:35:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我总是摇摆不定
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.26,0:35:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是坦然地面对他人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.06,0:35:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很羡慕你这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.15,0:35:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.65,0:35:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是觉得重要的东西 就越是会回避
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.70,0:35:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的归来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.41,0:35:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我又得以靠近仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.83,0:35:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是为了向你道歉才想实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.67,0:36:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知从什么时候 不知从什么时候起 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.72,0:36:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,257)}今天和大家一起玩了 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.85,0:36:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(614,257)}今天和大家一起玩了 很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.82,0:36:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.07,0:36:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好随便
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.11,0:36:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了「很有趣」「很高兴」 就没别的不同了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.24,0:36:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 很不擅长写作文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.33,0:36:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这里稍微不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.62,0:36:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「今天和大家一起玩时摔倒了 好痛」
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.96,0:36:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这里也不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.00,0:36:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「今天和大家一起去探望仁碳妈妈了」
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.92,0:36:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探望…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.84,0:36:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 还真是经常去呢 大家结伴一起
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.02,0:36:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.39,0:36:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳的妈妈一直在医院呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.69,0:36:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 给神仙写信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.86,0:37:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「请让仁碳的妈妈早日恢复健康」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.61,0:37:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么给呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.41,0:37:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳 那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.55,0:37:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.76,0:37:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.38,0:37:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.50,0:37:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「大家决定一起做烟花了」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.39,0:37:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我觉得好难」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.43,0:37:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不过我会加油」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.77,0:37:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 想起来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.14,0:37:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「把信装在火箭烟花里 送给神仙吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.11,0:37:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 就是这个吧? 芽间的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.90,0:37:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.17,0:37:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.19,0:37:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候说要做 结果还是没做成
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.95,0:37:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.95,0:37:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了…我妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.54,0:37:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 我才察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.84,0:38:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁太的心意 还有我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.77,0:38:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你又增加兼职了?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因为体力活挣得比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.76,0:38:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色好像很不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.60,0:38:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因为没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.02,0:38:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.48,0:38:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直以来都是吃了就睡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.86,0:38:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡眠攒够了的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.47,0:38:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.57,0:38:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么能那么拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对芽间就那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.54,0:38:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 仁…仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.25,0:38:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你水
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.13,0:38:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个 营养剂
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.22,0:38:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先喝下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.47,0:38:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼…好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.72,0:38:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.93,0:38:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.23,0:38:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.35,0:39:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再这么做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.15,0:39:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳受的伤害也够多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.57,0:39:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再这样了 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.44,0:39:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是哪样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.66,0:39:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在工作中呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.46,0:39:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要你走
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.75,0:39:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.79,0:39:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.34,0:39:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不想你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.51,0:39:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那时候」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.30,0:39:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.26,0:39:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要说些很差劲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.31,0:39:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 其实我松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.10,0:39:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳说不喜欢芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.53,0:39:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很过分 但是真的有点儿开心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.82,0:39:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.29,0:40:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你像那样走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.63,0:40:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在说 你最喜欢芽间一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.05,0:40:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后一直很心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.51,0:40:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法原谅在那瞬间高兴的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.31,0:40:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害了芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.77,0:40:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.52,0:40:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.90,0:40:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法原谅喜欢仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.73,0:40:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…我…还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.21,0:40:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是要走么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.79,0:40:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.55,0:40:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算 芽间真的在仁碳那里
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.76,0:40:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.89,0:40:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间不就消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.51,0:40:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间消失你无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.14,0:41:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明喜欢她的!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.06,0:41:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.77,0:41:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.53,0:41:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.03,0:41:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.08,0:41:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是 真是 真是 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.71,0:41:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是笨蛋 不是都很清楚了吗 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.38,0:41:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 没错 我就是笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.34,0:41:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.51,0:41:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.89,0:41:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.98,0:41:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.40,0:41:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都出了那么大的丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.19,0:41:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆出丑到底 落得个轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.36,0:41:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(不知从什么时候 不知从什么时候起 我喜欢上了仁碳)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.57,0:41:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.45,0:42:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.41,0:42:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.20,0:42:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 手帕…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.16,0:42:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.04,0:42:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是什么事 不过别太自责
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.59,0:42:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 说自己是笨蛋什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.51,0:42:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 这包薯条没事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.43,0:42:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 你才不是笨蛋 长得就很聪明的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.80,0:42:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.81,0:42:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.73,0:42:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得还缺了点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.74,0:42:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是在迷惘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.87,0:42:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那时并不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.29,0:42:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.88,0:42:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.64,0:43:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我们总是在迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.07,0:43:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.52,0:43:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我们想要尽可能减少迷惘 想要清晰的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.36,0:43:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群家伙 为啥不来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.53,0:43:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,120)}{\c&H3842BB&}再{\c&H538BEC&}见{\c&H4FFFF0&}了 {\c&H51B25B&}芽{\c&HA07E37&}间
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.65,0:43:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 反正明天也会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.32,0:43:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.28,0:43:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫他们!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.58,0:43:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎? 喂 波波!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.45,0:43:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.95,0:43:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤见子!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.37,0:43:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买了些点心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.87,0:43:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦! 不愧是鹤见子!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.29,0:43:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.59,0:43:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦! 爱死你了 雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.63,0:43:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}哇! 开party啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.18,0:43:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}Party party…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.09,0:43:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信的! 我真的是相信你们的!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.64,0:43:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心死我了 真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.22,0:43:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦! 我爱死这个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.89,0:43:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又聚在一起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.48,0:43:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.35,0:43:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.69,0:43:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉…离结束越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.65,0:44:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 芽间和我们 组成了「超和平Busters」…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.20,0:44:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开场白就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.70,0:44:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.58,0:44:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请主角芽间 上前来!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.87,0:44:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.43,0:44:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}(谢谢大家今天为了芽间而来)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.63,0:44:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.90,0:44:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}(芽间明天就要成佛了)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.05,0:44:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(422,132)}直到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.05,0:44:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(922,158)}也想跟大家
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.05,0:44:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(405,305)}继续
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.05,0:44:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(913,333)}做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.05,0:44:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(413,493)}请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.98,0:44:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢芽间的致辞!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.07,0:44:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间 吃这个不?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.86,0:44:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红通通的 辣的东西吃起来喉咙疼 不干!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.62,0:44:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…「辣的」…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.58,0:44:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}没这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.16,0:44:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}没问题的 吃一口试试啦 张嘴啦 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.58,0:44:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}嘴巴好辣…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.71,0:44:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么余兴节目么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.42,0:44:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.46,0:44:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不就变成吃喝大会了么 这是誓师大会吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.76,0:45:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会难得 来搞点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.42,0:45:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.80,0:45:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,余兴节目…要搞什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.80,0:45:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.68,0:45:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再搞一次 那一天的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.72,0:45:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.52,0:45:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 在这里发生的事情 重现一次如何
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.15,0:45:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说「在这里发生的事情」…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.32,0:45:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.15,0:45:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑! 做这种事有什么意义…!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.66,0:45:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安鸣!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.66,0:45:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁…仁碳你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.71,0:45:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.12,0:45:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢芽间…吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.63,0:45:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.67,0:45:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.13,0:45:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间也在这里吧? 给我清楚地说出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.59,0:45:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪集…!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.60,0:45:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.35,0:45:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊…说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.56,0:46:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 说啊 说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.61,0:46:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}说啊 说啊 说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.03,0:46:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等! 这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.36,0:46:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用做得这么过分吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.03,0:46:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}说啊 说啊 说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.71,0:46:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.46,0:46:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…对芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.68,0:46:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的话 一切就跟那时一样了! 仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.32,0:46:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在总是迷惘的我们之中
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.57,0:46:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳显得特别坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.99,0:46:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说不愧是头儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.41,0:47:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 芽间你才在他的面前出现的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.67,0:47:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还有点事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.51,0:47:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.85,0:47:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.68,0:47:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.06,0:47:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裤袋妖怪和外人的意思是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.35,0:47:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.32,0:47:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外人不是指外国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.57,0:47:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会跟皮皮顿一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.16,0:47:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳你知道外人的汉字怎么写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.00,0:47:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.58,0:47:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是「外面的人」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.25,0:47:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.29,0:47:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你知道裤袋妖怪是什么意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.34,0:47:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裤袋妖怪 是「在外面 进不到里面」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.34,0:47:54.14,note,NTP,0,0,0,,注：裤袋妖怪的发音在日语中表示被排挤、排斥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.30,0:47:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.18,0:47:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.98,0:47:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.06,0:48:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间就是进不来的外人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.52,0:48:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为芽间是外面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.94,0:48:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是不能进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.99,0:48:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能进学校和家里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.78,0:48:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要睡在邻居家小狗的窝里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.45,0:48:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那里是外面
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.79,0:48:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只小狗总是对着芽间叫
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.83,0:48:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道能不能和它做好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.38,0:48:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会不会咬我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.80,0:48:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.18,0:48:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国语课上布置的作业不是让我们写故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.98,0:48:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.40,0:48:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进不来的外人 芽间想象的故事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.82,0:48:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.49,0:48:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有秘密基地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.70,0:49:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超和平Busters的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.46,0:49:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家随时都能回去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.13,0:49:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.39,0:49:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.31,0:49:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.31,0:49:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.35,0:49:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面昨天吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.44,0:49:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就猪排饭?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.36,0:49:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.86,0:49:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大块猪排就是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.28,0:49:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 仁碳 刚才跟着起哄了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.70,0:49:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.95,0:49:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得 一切都像回到了从前一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.79,0:49:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到从前…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.21,0:49:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.67,0:49:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是真心的?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.05,0:49:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是真…的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.72,0:49:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间也喜欢仁碳～
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.35,0:50:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽 虽说是喜欢…不过不只是朋友间的那种喜欢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.85,0:50:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啊 是想让我嫁给你的那种喜欢吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.31,0:50:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间我啊 要是也能普普通通地像这样长大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.07,0:50:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会 成为仁碳的妻子呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.03,0:50:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不是…普通地…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.75,0:50:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不成佛 像现在这样留下来不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.34,0:50:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.46,0:50:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.56,0:50:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会成佛的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.31,0:50:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为啊 我会转世的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.90,0:50:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不成佛的话 就没办法转世了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.07,0:50:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能跟大家一起好好地聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.11,0:50:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}但是 如果变成了青虫的话怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.15,0:51:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 你清楚地做出了选择
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.99,0:51:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没出息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.50,0:51:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.04,0:51:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 明明是我叫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.08,0:51:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 我也刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.63,0:51:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 哎呀 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.01,0:51:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.80,0:51:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.97,0:51:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是仁太前辈没长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.80,0:51:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我仁太前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.93,0:51:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.77,0:51:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.23,0:51:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把这个给芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.94,0:51:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给供到你姐姐的佛坛前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.82,0:51:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是蒸面包?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.20,0:51:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.61,0:51:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让老爸教我做了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.62,0:51:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 不是这样啦 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.41,0:51:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 不是放进发酵粉就会发起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.46,0:51:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔子的蒸面包的美味秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.29,0:51:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个 松饼粉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.92,0:51:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 松饼?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.63,0:52:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也可以用来做蒸面包
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.97,0:52:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看背面 背面 蒸面包的食谱也印在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.56,0:52:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.02,0:52:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到老妈还挺会偷懒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.43,0:52:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太会做菜也是塔子的可爱之处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.86,0:52:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实还挺容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.65,0:52:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好像很好吃耶
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.15,0:52:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你直接到我家来就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.45,0:52:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈他们也已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.20,0:52:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.92,0:52:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我会和大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.58,0:52:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 超和平Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.13,0:52:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.54,0:52:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.55,0:52:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.39,0:52:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没戏 也说出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.73,0:53:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 多亏了芽间 大家好不容易又要好了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.90,0:53:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是又闹出尴尬…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.28,0:53:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安鸣?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.33,0:53:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.50,0:53:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去基地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.67,0:53:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯 肯定会去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.46,0:53:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发什么火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.50,0:53:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.67,0:53:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.77,0:53:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳你是不是又长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.86,0:53:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像已经不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.11,0:53:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.07,0:53:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.99,0:53:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你不穿像凶器一样的鞋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.99,0:53:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 什么凶器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.79,0:53:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 肯定长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.17,0:54:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.13,0:54:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.26,0:54:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.09,0:54:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你信写好了吗? 信纸三张
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.05,0:54:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三张? 还有那种指标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.59,0:54:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.47,0:54:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}这种事心意是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.93,0:54:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.73,0:54:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}最少也要三张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.23,0:54:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自己才只写了一张
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.94,0:54:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.69,0:54:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要情意是真的 几张都没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.66,0:54:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.59,0:54:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.38,0:54:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那个夏天...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.08,0:54:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}你真是什么都不懂啊 所以才总是不及格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.56,0:54:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}跟这个有什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.45,0:54:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论经历多少次夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.41,0:54:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.83,0:54:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 只有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.52,0:55:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 再给我点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.69,0:55:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要为我放烟花 所以 再给我点时间…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.91,0:55:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳 安鸣 你们好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.29,0:55:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 我们两个是最后了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.87,0:55:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.21,0:55:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.88,0:55:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超和平Busters 到齐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.92,0:55:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤见子你要不要驱虫剂?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.80,0:55:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经涂过好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.13,0:55:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 用这个搞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.34,0:55:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.72,0:55:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才说虽然有点那啥 不过还真传统啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.43,0:55:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛 就当是芽间的第一次盂兰盆会
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.86,0:55:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算第一次盂兰盆会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.69,0:55:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 现在外面还亮得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.32,0:55:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事不是应该在夜空下做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.41,0:55:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.91,0:55:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失策
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.87,0:55:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在等你们的时候做烧烤的准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.54,0:56:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是什么事都不离烧烤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.54,0:56:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.21,0:56:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.09,0:56:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.30,0:56:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么烟花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.72,0:56:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 安鸣 这可是你拿来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.68,0:56:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是上次烧烤的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.52,0:56:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.00,0:56:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时因为雪集做了奇怪的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.37,0:56:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.03,0:56:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.24,0:56:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.24,0:56:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.99,0:56:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得大家又聚在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.37,0:56:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大玩特玩一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.70,0:56:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.83,0:56:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这地方大家经常来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.17,0:56:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是聚得这么齐还真是很久没有过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.63,0:56:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.05,0:56:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起白天祭信
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.67,0:56:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天放烟花不是更奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.13,0:56:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.84,0:56:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭烟花在白天放更有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.97,0:56:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年不也是大白天的放了一个超大的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.68,0:57:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 那个可壮观了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.06,0:57:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是花了好多钱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.48,0:57:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.27,0:57:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.03,0:57:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽间也会高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.28,0:57:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们放了烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.27,0:57:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相信那个烟花是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.24,0:57:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.95,0:57:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～! 花儿在天空绽放了～
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.91,0:58:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.12,0:58:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.58,0:58:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.75,0:58:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芽…间…?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.00,0:58:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.88,0:58:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}咦 点不着耶
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.26,0:58:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时明明应该很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.18,0:58:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}毕竟都是去年的了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.76,0:58:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却莫名松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.46,0:58:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}不 这种事要看气势
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.64,0:58:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.02,0:58:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安鸣 再拿一个来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.31,0:58:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对芽间的愿望没了头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.65,0:58:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的心情无从排遣
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.28,0:58:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们都只能向着自己心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.16,0:58:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一直藏在心底的感情化作怒吼 号叫
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.80,0:58:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.38,0:58:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.43,0:58:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要道歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.22,0:59:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.35,0:59:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳想怎样都随他去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.27,0:59:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好地向芽间道歉 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.77,0:59:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安…安鸣?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.83,0:59:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦?!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.81,0:59:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睫毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.40,0:59:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.15,0:59:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了! 假睫毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.49,0:59:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.65,0:59:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 我就觉得安鸣的眼睛不一样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.45,0:59:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤见子 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.78,0:59:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就够密的了 根本没必要弄假的吧 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.25,0:59:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安鸣保持这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.25,0:59:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 谢谢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.04,0:59:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不准再「安鸣 安鸣」地叫了!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.00,0:59:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.09,0:59:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都叫回外号了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.26,0:59:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.43,0:59:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雪集说的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.56,0:59:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.44,0:59:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的内心某处 其实在为只有自己能看到芽间而高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.77,0:59:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.78,0:59:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 芽间不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.24,1:00:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢 我倒希望她不要成佛的好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.37,1:00:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.75,1:00:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只和我 还想和大家一起好好说话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.96,1:00:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想要成佛转世
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.17,1:00:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地实现芽间的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.93,1:00:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把芽间也叫来 用日记好好和她谈谈
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.93,1:00:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和芽间一起 再一次…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.06,1:00:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 芽间不在说什么都没有意义 因为…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.65,1:00:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们六人合在一起…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.77,1:00:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是「超和平Busters」啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.32,1:00:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.03,1:00:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这是我想说的话啊…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.49,1:00:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.12,1:00:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.53,1:00:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.99,1:00:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上把芽间带过来 去秘密基地集合吧!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.04,1:00:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别玩了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.03,1:00:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还差一点就着了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.67,1:01:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话你刚才就说过
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.05,1:01:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 头儿
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.97,1:01:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 头儿是…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.59,1:01:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在打工吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.47,1:01:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再叫我头儿了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.43,1:01:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩游戏店了 多少做一点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.39,1:01:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校呢 不会留级吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.44,1:01:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是有算好出勤数的 勉强还说得过去…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.44,1:01:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你们别两面夹击我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.03,1:01:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要这么要好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.49,1:01:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.49,1:01:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这什么反应
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.58,1:01:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.58,1:01:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊? 什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.79,1:01:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你们 快帮我阻止波波啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.79,1:01:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话 给我啦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.88,1:01:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加点火力就…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.71,1:01:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们小心点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.34,1:01:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也该放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.38,1:01:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃了不就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.72,1:01:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪里的篮球教练啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.31,1:01:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁碳 好慢啊…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.10,1:01:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是在和大家玩呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.85,1:01:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.07,1:02:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 芽间现在这个样子
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.77,1:02:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去了也只会妨碍大家呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.24,1:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.16,1:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能再见到大家 芽间真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.17,1:02:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然最后想好好道个别 但是…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.05,1:02:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳果然…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.77,1:02:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.90,1:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.32,1:02:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.37,1:02:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 芽间…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.50,1:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 怎么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.87,1:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间的愿望 好像…已经实现了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.84,1:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间想起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.42,1:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,和仁碳的妈妈约定的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.18,1:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,和…妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.64,1:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.22,1:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.37,1:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.27,1:03:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,仁太从来不哭
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.81,1:03:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是因为我变成这样了 所以一直撑着
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.98,1:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.40,1:03:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然转世投胎也不错
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.24,1:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过只有这件事我放不下
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.24,1:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,害他一直在忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.16,1:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 我很希望他能多笑一点 多生点气 多哭一点…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.25,1:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.09,1:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间和你约定 绝对要让仁碳哭出来!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.85,1:03:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.39,1:03:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了 小芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.31,1:04:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.98,1:04:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.11,1:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是呢…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.28,1:04:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然芽间考虑了很多
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.49,1:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是完全不知道该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.28,1:04:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.58,1:04:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就想拜托大家帮忙
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.41,1:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,于是打电话把大家集合起来…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.08,1:04:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs38}但并不是让大家欺负你让你哭哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.29,1:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.67,1:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜回到这里…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.01,1:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也要实现的…愿望…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.71,1:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}芽间不是很聪明
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.21,1:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}不使坏就能把你弄哭的方法 或许大家会知道
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.59,1:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}所以那天…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.10,1:04:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 还是…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.22,1:04:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不太顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.23,1:04:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是因为对仁碳保密…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.19,1:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以遭到惩罚了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.73,1:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是什么惩罚呢!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.61,1:04:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是会去的 保不保密又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.45,1:04:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不管什么时候 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.78,1:04:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我都会去那个地方的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.08,1:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳 又哭了…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.83,1:05:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 芽间其实更喜欢仁碳的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.13,1:05:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.88,1:05:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到说再见的时间了吗…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.72,1:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.72,1:05:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行 给我等一下!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.35,1:05:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我的话不行!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.64,1:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我…很想见你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.48,1:05:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很想见你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.57,1:05:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想呼唤你的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.11,1:05:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.70,1:05:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,想说喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.07,1:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.91,1:05:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 大家也是一样!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.03,1:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很喜欢你!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.41,1:05:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很想见你!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.33,1:05:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在等着你…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.83,1:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我们啊!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.79,1:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个…属于我们的地方!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.70,1:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.00,1:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.92,1:06:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢仁碳了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.63,1:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 这么突然地…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.13,1:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间 很高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.80,1:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想…永远和你…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.76,1:06:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.76,1:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至想和仁碳一起 一直这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.60,1:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.52,1:06:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.65,1:06:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.98,1:06:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.99,1:06:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…芽间!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.24,1:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.95,1:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,给 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.91,1:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.83,1:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 太阳一直不下山呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.96,1:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.42,1:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来 烟花也全废了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.59,1:07:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 只能乖乖等了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.55,1:07:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 鹤见子
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.34,1:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.05,1:07:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 是芽间的马克杯吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.56,1:07:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊 她好像很喜欢这种的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.73,1:07:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我却完全没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.44,1:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.11,1:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就连我 在芽间还在世的时候 也没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.90,1:07:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就连想都没想过
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.26,1:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然是怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.29,1:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,机会难得 在等天黑的时间里 大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.79,1:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来玩捉迷藏吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.04,1:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有能够马上回答
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.72,1:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,「为什么波波会提议做这种事」
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.34,1:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里明白 虽然很讨厌 但却明白
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.15,1:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.02,1:08:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.62,1:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.71,1:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,波波你总是先出石头啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.96,1:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,从以前就一直没变啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.95,1:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是很好懂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.16,1:08:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了 可恶
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.76,1:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.39,1:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我在玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.85,1:08:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,捉迷藏是什么意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.94,1:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.81,1:08:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs38}喂 芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.03,1:08:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间在玩捉迷藏吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.48,1:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,捉迷藏?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.07,1:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.28,1:09:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.24,1:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.95,1:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.41,1:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.07,1:09:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.74,1:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 玩了捉迷藏的话…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.46,1:09:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛就能见到…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.50,1:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其实就在这里 我们却一直看不到的芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.84,1:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 若是玩起捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.68,1:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛就能见到
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.85,1:09:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不光是我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.06,1:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,超和平Busters的大家 每个人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.02,1:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.65,1:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间似乎也会重新回到这里
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.11,1:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,500)}超和平Busters 永远都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.45,1:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}超和平Busters
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.08,1:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行…还不可以走…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.55,1:10:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有…好好地…道别呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.05,1:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.64,1:10:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还没好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.98,1:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有… 大家都在等我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.15,1:10:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间也要 好好地
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.45,1:10:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.79,1:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.83,1:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间觉得雪集的女装很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.97,1:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 雪集的心灵也很美丽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.73,1:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,安鸣
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.15,1:11:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}芽间…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.81,1:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个可靠 热心的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.65,1:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,跟安鸣在一起的时候 芽间我会撒娇哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.62,1:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤见子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.12,1:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.04,1:11:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一直对芽间很温柔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.17,1:11:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有来世 芽间我想成为鹤见子这样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.43,1:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.51,1:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,波波
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.89,1:11:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直是大家的开心果
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.44,1:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间笑得肚子都疼了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.50,1:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然 芽间跟大家在一起很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.63,1:12:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,却发现了一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.67,1:12:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是因为芽间 才让大家沉浸在悲伤的气氛里
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.35,1:12:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,明明自己一直以来 都在模仿着本间芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.89,1:12:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不准你随便拿死去女孩的名字来说事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.94,1:12:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间要是出现的话
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.65,1:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,应该出现在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.24,1:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,变鬼也好 诅咒也好
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.99,1:12:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也该…也该在我的面前!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.33,1:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要只在仁碳面前
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.25,1:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也在我的面前现个身吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.87,1:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你姐姐有些吊儿郎当
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.46,1:12:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定都没有察觉到自己已经死了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.42,1:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你差不多该放过我了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.01,1:12:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你在一起 我想起的尽是烦心事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.60,1:12:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,尽是不愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.35,1:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很烦躁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.56,1:13:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间已经不希望大家因为我而伤心了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.45,1:13:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.49,1:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.99,1:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你对芽间发了很大的火呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.75,1:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给我适可而止吧!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.70,1:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这样只考虑别人的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.98,1:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,多考虑一下自己的事情啊!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.30,1:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,让人替你着急啊 你那态度
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.55,1:13:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,明明自己很难过
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.61,1:13:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,却还强颜欢笑
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.27,1:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,每次哭都是为了别人
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.85,1:13:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我…会这么愤怒?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.27,1:13:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.81,1:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.11,1:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间我一直都不知道 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.03,1:14:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳为了实现我的愿望 一直在努力着
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.54,1:14:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,新人 那边!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.17,1:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.55,1:14:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.22,1:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.05,1:14:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.97,1:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.35,1:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳他 可是很帅的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.82,1:14:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在芽间没有替自己着想的日子里
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.70,1:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳心里一直牵挂着芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.29,1:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 小心脚下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.67,1:14:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.18,1:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.35,1:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别随便变动灯光的方向
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.19,1:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.27,1:15:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为刮风?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.45,1:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,刮风就能改变灯光的方向吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.95,1:15:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,闪闪发光的仁碳 真帅气
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.54,1:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真帅气
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.96,1:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳为了芽间 拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.76,1:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以芽间就快想起自己的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.43,1:15:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.65,1:15:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.90,1:15:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.69,1:15:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.46,1:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,指甲好黑
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.75,1:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿牙签给你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.42,1:16:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 不用啦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.59,1:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要给你弄
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.63,1:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.51,1:16:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果实现了愿望 芽间就会…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.26,1:16:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.01,1:16:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 再一下下
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.56,1:16:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那是芽间所期望的事
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.78,1:16:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我就…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.49,1:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.58,1:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.70,1:16:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么痛吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.41,1:16:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.79,1:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起「弗兰德斯的狗」了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.30,1:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,帕… 帕特拉什的故事
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.05,1:17:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特拉什?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.47,1:17:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰德斯的…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.80,1:17:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,以前…重播过的那个…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.56,1:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊…这谎撒得太烂了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.73,1:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.61,1:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.36,1:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.61,1:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得帕特拉什 一定过得很幸福的!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.90,1:17:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.24,1:17:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为耐罗对它非常非常好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.83,1:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,又是好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.54,1:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.51,1:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.02,1:18:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间的愿望 就是仁碳的妈妈的愿望
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.66,1:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好想实现它 芽间好想让仁碳哭出来
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.59,1:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那一天
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.88,1:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳拉起了我的手
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.35,1:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.97,1:18:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳跟芽间约好了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.77,1:18:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是有秘密基地的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.17,1:18:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,超和平Busters的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.90,1:18:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大家随时都能回去的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.58,1:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.25,1:19:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间才来到了仁碳的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.67,1:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.14,1:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还没好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.44,1:19:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再…稍微等下…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.41,1:19:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还…差一点…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.13,1:19:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.34,1:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 找到芽间…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.84,1:19:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你那脚…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.30,1:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.97,1:19:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 芽间已经…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.82,1:20:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.36,1:20:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.62,1:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,日记本的…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.73,1:20:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这字迹…是芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.07,1:20:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.71,1:20:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,「给鹤见子 最喜欢温柔的鹤见子了」
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.92,1:20:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,芽…间…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.21,1:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,「给雪集 最喜欢努力奋斗的雪集了」
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.93,1:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,「给波波 最喜欢有趣的波波了」
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.89,1:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,「给安鸣 最喜欢可靠的安鸣了」
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.03,1:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,「最喜欢仁碳了 对仁碳的喜欢是 想要成为仁碳新娘的那种喜欢哦」
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.33,1:20:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,赶上…了…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.95,1:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这次总算…好好地…道别了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.13,1:21:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.71,1:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么啊 芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.92,1:21:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在玩捉迷藏么?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.88,1:21:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话 不把你找出来…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.51,1:21:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就不算结束了啊!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.72,1:21:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.33,1:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,藏好了没?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.77,1:21:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,藏好了没?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.22,1:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,藏好了没 藏好了没…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.33,1:21:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,已经藏好了哦…!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.09,1:21:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的声音是…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.30,1:21:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.51,1:21:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,芽…间…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.85,1:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.64,1:22:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是…芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.69,1:22:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…是芽间啊!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.11,1:22:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.02,1:22:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.11,1:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间!芽间!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.69,1:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你了 芽间…!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.45,1:22:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.33,1:22:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候 不应该喊名字吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.95,1:22:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.75,1:22:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间还真是不擅长捉迷藏呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.13,1:22:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 仁碳 好好说一声吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.21,1:22:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.71,1:22:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这样…就能结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.77,1:22:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的信 我已经读了!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.89,1:22:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我也最喜欢你了 芽间!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.81,1:22:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也最喜欢你了!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.23,1:22:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也最喜欢你了!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.07,1:22:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然也最喜欢你了!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.53,1:23:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,道别 可不能光听不说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.45,1:23:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.04,1:23:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,愿望已经达成了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.38,1:23:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢你了 芽间!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.18,1:23:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.52,1:23:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.31,1:23:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.19,1:23:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,牵住芽间的仁碳的手
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.40,1:23:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等待着芽间的 大家的笑容
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.78,1:23:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳芽间 找到你们了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.58,1:23:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.04,1:23:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}接下来玩什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.33,1:23:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为你慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.58,1:23:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.09,1:23:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,狗窝可不行…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.88,1:24:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就是作业里那个「进不来的外人」的故事
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.60,1:24:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你睡在狗窝里
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.28,1:24:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你去到哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.85,1:24:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对有人会找到你
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.52,1:24:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,给我记住啦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.90,1:24:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.53,1:24:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.20,1:24:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳又把芽间弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.79,1:24:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.87,1:24:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.37,1:24:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.16,1:24:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,弄哭了 弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.46,1:24:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉老师～
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.04,1:24:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,波波你这个叛徒!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.88,1:24:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳 你这样不对的!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.92,1:24:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.92,1:24:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了 波波!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.26,1:24:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.55,1:24:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.72,1:24:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间 记得你说的话
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.31,1:24:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,无论何时 超和平Busters的大家
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.72,1:24:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都能把芽间找出来
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.94,1:24:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.86,1:25:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间我…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.53,1:25:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还想…继续和大家在一起…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.62,1:25:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想和大家一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.16,1:25:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 要转世投胎…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.54,1:25:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,重新…和大家相聚…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.34,1:25:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.22,1:25:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳…也哭过了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.51,1:25:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要…和大家告别了…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.18,1:25:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.48,1:25:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一二…!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.40,1:25:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间 找到你了!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.49,1:25:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,被找到了…呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.66,1:25:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间…果然…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.28,1:26:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…一直…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.83,1:26:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢你们了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.50,1:26:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,藏好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.25,1:26:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.22,1:26:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 抓紧时间啦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.34,1:26:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,藏好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.72,1:26:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.56,1:26:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,躲好了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.48,1:26:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 赶紧挪一挪!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.35,1:26:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 为什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.19,1:26:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲到别的地方去!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.23,1:27:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间啦 快点
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.15,1:27:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.07,1:27:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看我把你们一个不剩地全找出来
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.61,1:27:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这边!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.04,1:27:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,走了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.58,1:27:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.96,1:27:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那个… 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.68,1:27:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.04,1:27:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}(超和平busters永远都是好朋友)
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.39,1:27:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是这个…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.27,1:27:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.40,1:27:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我母亲的嘱托
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.40,1:27:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而是芽间 她自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.16,1:27:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.37,1:27:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.33,1:27:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.08,1:28:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.18,1:28:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你… 这还在玩捉迷藏呢 竟然做出这么大胆的举动…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.31,1:28:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 发现安鸣
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.43,1:28:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这个声音
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.31,1:28:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,找到仁碳了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.36,1:28:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.94,1:28:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 安鸣 这都怨你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.48,1:28:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 安鸣 接下来该你…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.65,1:28:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.24,1:28:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.07,1:28:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哈什么啊 你们两个都给我出去
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.45,1:28:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.87,1:28:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 两个色鬼滚出去
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.92,1:28:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.00,1:28:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,色鬼?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.21,1:28:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别管了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.21,1:28:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.96,1:28:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,女人发起火来很恐怖 这句话似乎是真的…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.57,1:29:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.60,1:29:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.81,1:29:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.06,1:29:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你收到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.94,1:29:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}给个答复Please
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.69,1:29:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}用快递 用快递
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.70,1:29:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}到付的也行哦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.15,1:29:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再扇猛点啊 头儿
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.56,1:29:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你说了别这么叫
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.53,1:29:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}那啥 到付得花多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.16,1:29:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.33,1:30:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已经把自己非说不可的话 写到信上了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.96,1:30:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,「我喜欢仁碳」
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.88,1:30:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,「一直瞒着你 对不起」
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.80,1:30:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那你对仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.93,1:30:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我果然还是没法对仁碳开口
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.81,1:30:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.03,1:30:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.65,1:30:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.40,1:30:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,同样喜欢着喜欢芽间的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.90,1:30:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.70,1:30:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.20,1:30:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直都会是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.37,1:30:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是那个夏天
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.08,1:30:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还是这个夏天
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.83,1:30:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一直做朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.25,1:30:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,将来总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.38,1:30:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能将自己的感情传达出来的那个夏天 一定会到来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.93,1:31:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会被我抢先哟
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.10,1:31:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.27,1:31:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.19,1:31:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思 你们俩到底…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.69,1:31:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.19,1:31:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩说什么悄悄话呐
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.46,1:31:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让我也参与下嘛 Girls' talk
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.97,1:31:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.48,1:31:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真服了他们 又闹起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.71,1:31:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}有什么不好嘛 带我一个嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.72,1:31:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}都说不要了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.25,1:31:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,即便你不在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.55,1:31:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只要想起 你曾经与我们一同走过
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.97,1:31:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就感觉 平常的景色都变得不同了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.55,1:31:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得点点小事都弥足珍贵
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.38,1:31:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得绝对不能失去它们
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.26,1:31:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.36,1:31:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,星星好多
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.02,1:31:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.48,1:31:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里能看到这么多星星 真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.95,1:32:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们什么都没有失去…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.54,1:32:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 波波
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.87,1:32:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是来自芽间的回信哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.15,1:32:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟 真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.95,1:32:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.12,1:32:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能一脸正经地说出这番话…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.22,1:32:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真有点头儿的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.93,1:32:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这话什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.97,1:32:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 别叫我头儿…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.68,1:32:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是头儿
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.85,1:32:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.50,1:32:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的回信我们收到了哦!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.90,1:32:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.36,1:32:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,明年的今天 也像现在这样在这里集合吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.20,1:32:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 雪集 说得好
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.92,1:32:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,明年要高考吧 估计没空哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.37,1:32:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.87,1:32:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳无论何时都闲得要死啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.08,1:32:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.67,1:32:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里闲啦?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.96,1:32:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,仁碳有在升级哦!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.59,1:32:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛老说我的事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.17,1:32:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,升级不是很正常的嘛!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.76,1:33:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这是哪里来的?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.56,1:33:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,蒸面包?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.35,1:33:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这些 是今天我从别人那里拿到的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.98,1:33:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,从姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.45,1:33:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.20,1:33:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟那些孩子们说 到家里来给芽间上柱香吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.41,1:33:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.70,1:33:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.45,1:33:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 照片上的姐姐 是不是在笑啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.96,1:33:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是本来就在笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.84,1:33:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽没错啦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.21,1:33:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉比平时更灿烂了20%
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.17,1:33:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 快去洗澡啦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.84,1:33:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.30,1:38:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果转世重生
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.37,1:38:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要变成什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.79,1:38:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成花儿吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.96,1:38:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成蝴蝶吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.26,1:38:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成蚂蚁吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.47,1:38:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成芋头吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.60,1:38:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成什么都没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.77,1:38:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.94,1:39:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超和平Busters 永远都是好朋友

